===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Hapu (Masters)}}
Hapu forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Hapu|Mudsdale}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Hapu became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with her joining the {{player}} after completing the 10th chapter of the [[PML arc]]. 

In this game, Hapu is one of the PML Leaders of the [[Pokémon Masters League]], handing out the {{badge|Pride}} to those who defeat her.

